 The girl was rushed to hospital by her father following the invasion during which she and three others were held at gunpoint inside the Eastdene home.
Four robbers entered the house around 11:00.
They fled the scene after wounding the lady in her 20’s. A notice has been sent out on media platforms with surveillance footage of the alleged suspects, asking anyone with information that could help lead to the arrest of the suspects to contact the Middelburg SAPS or Mr Aroon Bhayat at 072 280 3121. One of two men caught on surveillance footage.   surveillance footage of the vehicle implicated in the crime.  Dullstroom farm attack trial postponed VIDEO: Dance group brings joy to residents Middelburg weekly weather forecast Pay or use ‘The road where death lives’  • Save our standby number (072 248 3855) and send us a WhatsApp message with the words “Add me” to be added to our broadcast list. • Like us on Facebook, follow us on Twitter and Instagram. • Subscribe to our YouTube channel. • Click on the link to subscribe to our bi-weekly newsletter via email. Contact our news room on our 24 hr standby number 072 248 3855, or send a mail to our editor tobie@mobserver.co.za